parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the alternator can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, and leave the driver stranded, which can lead to accidents or other safety risks.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power while driving
the battery charging system light comes on
the ABS light flashes
the airbag light comes on
the vehicle makes a loud noise
smoke comes from under the hood
the alternator overheats
and the vehicle is unable to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the smart glass switch can cause the driver's side window to malfunction, drain the battery, and prevent the vehicle from starting, which can lead to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The driver's side window operates independently
the window rolls up and down on its own
the battery drains
the vehicle is unable to start
and the trunk release is inoperable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, and experience various electrical malfunctions, which can lead to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power while driving
various warning lights illuminate
the vehicle experiences electrical malfunctions
and the battery drains.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag wiring harness connector can cause the airbag to malfunction or not deploy in the event of an accident, leading to increased risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag may not deploy in an accident
the light may flash on and off
and the airbag system may be disabled.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Takata airbag inflator can cause the airbag to rupture or underinflate, leading to increased risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag may not deploy in an accident
and the airbag system may be disabled.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the airbag system can cause the airbag to malfunction or not deploy in the event of an accident, leading to increased risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates intermittently
the airbag may not deploy in an accident
and the airbag system may be disabled intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Fuel leaks and fuel odor can cause a fire hazard, explosion, and health risks, especially when the fuel tank is near the exhaust system, which is hot and can ignite the fuel.
symptoms: Strong fuel smell inside the cabin
fuel leaking under the rear passenger side
fuel puddles under the back seat
fuel dripping onto the ground
fuel odor in the trunk
fuel rail leaking at the seam
fuel injector O-ring failure.
